'''貝迪治'''（'''Zakarya Bergdich'''，{{lang-ar|زكرياء برݣديش}}，{{bd|1989年|1月7日||}}）是[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]的職業足球運動員，司職[[左後衛|左後衛]]，現效力於[[英格蘭冠軍足球聯賽|英格蘭冠軍足球聯賽]][[查爾頓體育足球會|查爾頓]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Morocco - Z. Bergdich - Profile with news, career statistics and history - Soccerway|url=http://uk.soccerway.com/players/zakarya-bergdich/156704/|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=28 July 2012|archive-date=2017-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813055930/http://uk.soccerway.com/players/zakarya-bergdich/156704/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=FOOTBALL Bergdich, fier d'être un Lensois|url=http://www.courrier-picard.fr/courrier/Sports/Sport-en-Picardie/Bergdich-fier-d-etre-un-Lensois|accessdate=28 July 2012|newspaper=Le Courrier picard|date=20 July 2011|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304122704/http://www.courrier-picard.fr/courrier/Sports/Sport-en-Picardie/Bergdich-fier-d-etre-un-Lensois|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Z. Bergdich: "Lens, la destination idéale"|url=http://www.lensois.com/articles/2126-z-bergdich-lens-la-destination-ideale|accessdate=28 July 2012|newspaper=Lensois|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629205943/http://www.lensois.com/articles/2126-z-bergdich-lens-la-destination-ideale|archivedate=2013年6月29日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Zakaria Bergdich rejoint la CFA lensoise|url=http://www.rclens.fr/infos_2010/06/30_cfa_bergdich/index.php#ancreContenu|accessdate=28 July 2012|newspaper=RC Lens|date=30 June 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203172203/http://www.rclens.fr/infos_2010/06/30_cfa_bergdich/index.php#ancreContenu|archive-date=2015-02-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

